lead_paragraph: Juventus ended a remarkable Inter Milan comeback by winning their Italian Cup tie 5-3 on penalties on Wednesday after their semi-final ended 3-3 on aggregate, setting up a final against AC Milan.

headline.print_headline: Juve Thwart Three-Goal Inter Comeback to Reach Final
